structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
PUBLIC WORKS IN CITIES OF THE FIRST CLASS (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 239, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1980. -- Section was merely a reference entry, to call attention to the fact that the provisions of KRS 94.281 to 94.287 applied to cities of the first class as well as other cities.
